RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: WHERE ROLE_FUNCTION IN (SELECT FUNCTION_ID FROM SMTB_MENU WHERE TYPE_STRING in('M' ,'D','BOTG','ELM','LNC','LNM','PMO','SM'))
WHERE ROLE_FUNCTION IN (SELECT FUNCTION_ID FROM SMTB_MENU WHERE TYPE_STRING IN('R','U','ELR'))
WHERE ROLE_FUNCTION IN (SELECT FUNCTION_ID FROM SMTB_MENU WHERE TYPE_STRING='B')
WHERE ROLE_FUNCTION IN (SELECT FUNCTION_ID FROM SMTB_MENU WHERE TYPE_STRING in ('O','ELO','PMO'))
WHERE ROLE_FUNCTION IN (SELECT FUNCTION_ID FROM SMTB_MENU WHERE TYPE_STRING IN ('P','T'))

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT FUNCTION_ID, BALOON_HELP FROM (SELECT A.FUNCTION_ID FUNCTION_ID, (SELECT DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION WHERE FUNCTION_ID = A.FUNCTION_ID AND LANG_CODE = GLOBAL.LANG) BALOON_HELP FROM SMTBS_MENU A, SMTBS_MODULES C WHERE A.TYPE_STRING IN ('SM','M', 'D','BOTG','ELM','LNC','LNM','PMO','GQ') AND A.MODULE = C.MODULE_ID and a.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND a.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND not exists (select 1 from smtb_default_dashboard df_dash where df_dash.db_functionid = a.function_id)) WHERE 1 = 1 ORDER BY FUNCTION_ID

SELECT FUNCTION_ID, BALOON_HELP FROM (SELECT A.FUNCTION_ID FUNCTION_ID, (SELECT DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION WHERE FUNCTION_ID = A.FUNCTION_ID AND LANG_CODE = GLOBAL.LANG ) BALOON_HELP FROM SMTBS_MENU A, SMTBS_MODULES C WHERE A.TYPE_STRING IN ('R', 'U', 'ELR') AND A.MODULE = C.MODULE_ID and a.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND a.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y') WHERE 1 = 1

SELECT FUNCTION_ID, BALOON_HELP FROM (SELECT A.FUNCTION_ID FUNCTION_ID, (SELECT DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION WHERE FUNCTION_ID = A.FUNCTION_ID AND LANG_CODE = 'ENG') BALOON_HELP FROM SMTBS_MENU A, SMTBS_MODULES C WHERE A.TYPE_STRING IN ('B') AND A.MODULE = C.MODULE_ID and a.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND a.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y') WHERE 1 = 1

SELECT distinct FUNCTION_ID, BALOON_HELP FROM (SELECT A.FUNCTION_ID FUNCTION_ID, (SELECT DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION WHERE FUNCTION_ID = A.FUNCTION_ID AND LANG_CODE = GLOBAL.LANG) BALOON_HELP FROM SMTBS_MENU A, SMTBS_MODULES C, SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION D WHERE A.TYPE_STRING IN ('O', 'ELO') AND SUBSTR(A.FUNCTION_ID, 3, 1) <> 'C' AND A.FUNCTION_ID = D.FUNCTION_ID AND A.MODULE = C.MODULE_ID and a.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND a.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y') WHERE 1 = 1
SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM STTM_CORE_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND ONCE_AUTH='Y'
SELECT QUEUE, DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_QUEUES WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND ONCE_AUTH='Y'

SELECT FUNCTION_ID, SUB_MENU_2, FUNCTION_LEVEL FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.FUNCTION_ID FUNCTION_ID, B.SUB_MENU_2 SUB_MENU_2, DECODE(A.AVAILABLE,0,'MENU ITEM',1,'EXECUTABLE') FUNCTION_LEVEL FROM SMTB_MENU A, SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION B WHERE A.TYPE_STRING IN ('WB') AND A.FUNCTION_ID=B.FUNCTION_ID AND B.LANG_CODE=GLOBAL.LANG AND A.MODULE=B.BRANCH_MODULE) WHERE 1 = 1
SELECT DISTINCT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTM_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND ONCE_AUTH='Y'

SELECT FUNCTION_ID, BALOON_HELP, PROCESS_DESC FROM (SELECT A.FUNCTION_ID FUNCTION_ID, (SELECT DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION WHERE FUNCTION_ID = A.FUNCTION_ID AND LANG_CODE = GLOBAL.LANG ) BALOON_HELP, (SELECT PROCESS_DESC FROM SMTM_PROCESS_CODES WHERE PROCESS_CODE = A.PROCESS_CODE) PROCESS_DESC FROM SMTBS_MENU A, SMTBS_MODULES C WHERE A.TYPE_STRING IN ('P', 'T') AND SUBSTR(A.FUNCTION_ID, 3, 1) <> 'C' AND A.MODULE = C.MODULE_ID and a.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND a.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y') WHERE 1 = 1

RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: WHERE ROLE_FUNCTION IN (SELECT FUNCTION_ID FROM SMTB_MENU WHERE TYPE_STRING='WB')

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT ROLE_ID, ROLE_DESCRIPTION FROM COTM_ROLE_DETAILS WHERE AUTH_STAT='A'
